    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2001 BMW M3 (E46) in concours-level condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to achieve a linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and the factory M-Variable differential lock for optimal torque distribution. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a documented VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring total structural and mechanical integrity. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, and the chassis remains free of any oxidation or fatigue. A turn-key masterpiece for the purist collector who demands peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
