      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a true collector's dream. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish, free of any swirl marks or stone chips, having been meticulously stored in a climate-controlled environment. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and pristine, showing zero signs of wear or fading. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Accompanied by a full, documented service history from authorized specialists, this car has been maintained with an open-wallet policy. From the immaculate engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this is the finest example currently available on the market.",
      "price": 46500.0,
