      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated zenith, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. The engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS variable valve timing system that has been professionally overhauled for precision timing. The chassis is structurally immaculate, with a reinforced rear subframe and a factory-spec suspension geometry that maintains its original kinematic integrity. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip and tactile feedback. Every seal, bushing, and fluid line is in showroom state, reflecting a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule. This vehicle remains in its original factory configuration, free of any aftermarket modifications or thermal fatigue.",
